```json
{
  "application": "PBS",
  "details": {
    "resource_requirements": {
      "nodes": 1,
      "cores_per_node": 8,
      "walltime": "0:45:00",
      "gres": "shifter",
      "allocation": "bbdz"
    },
    "software": {
      "modules": [
        "bash",
        "shifter"
      ],
      "shifter_image": "scailfin/delphes-python-centos:3.5.0"
    },
    "execution_environment": {
      "command": "aprun",
      "arguments": [
        "--bypass-app-transfer",
        "--pes-per-node",
        "1",
        "--cpu-binding",
        "none",
        "--",
        "shifter",
        "--clearenv",
        "--image=${SHIFTER_IMAGE}",
        "--volume=${OUTPUT_PATH}:/root/data",
        "--volume=/mnt/a/${HOME}:/mnt/a/${HOME}",
        "--env",
        "CODE_BASE_PATH=${CODE_BASE_PATH}",
        "--env",
        "INPUT_FILE=${INPUT_FILE}",
        "--env",
        "OUTPUT_PATH=${OUTPUT_PATH}",
        "--env",
        "OUTPUT_FILE=${OUTPUT_FILE}",
        "--workdir=/root/data",
        "--",
        "/bin/bash",
        "-c",
        "export LD_LIBRARY_PATH=$(echo -e \"${LD_LIBRARY_PATH//\:/\\n}\" | grep -v /opt/cray/nvidia/390.46-1_1.0502.2481.1.1.gem/lib64 | tr \"\\n\" \":\") && export PATH=\"/usr/local/venv/bin:${PATH}\" && printf \"\\n# printenv:\\n\" && printenv && printf \"\\n\\n\" && cp -r \"${CODE_BASE_PATH}\"/preprocessing \"${OUTPUT_PATH}\" && cd preprocessing && time bash run_preprocessing.sh \"${INPUT_FILE}\" \"${OUTPUT_FILE}\""
      ]
    }
  }
}
```
